---
import "../../styles/global.css";
import "./Soverview.css";
---

<section class="soverview-section">
  <div class="soverview-container">
    <h2 class="soverview-title">What’s Included With Membership</h2>

    <p class="soverview-subtitle">
      Broken Duck Studio is more than just a workspace. It’s a structured system designed to help YouTube creators make consistent, high-quality content — with the facilities, tools, and community to back it up.
    </p>

    <p class="soverview-subtitle">
      Every member gets 24/7 access to the studio, including use of voiceover booths, recording studios, office desks, and a private meeting room. Access is managed through a secure entry system and an online booking platform.
    </p>

    <div class="soverview-features">
      <div class="soverview-feature">12 hours per month in video studios</div>
      <div class="soverview-feature">12 hours per month in voiceover booths</div>
      <div class="soverview-feature">4 hours per month in the private meeting room</div>
      <div class="soverview-feature">Weekly Sunday workshops for creators</div>
      <div class="soverview-feature">Monthly public networking event (last Sunday of each month)</div>
      <div class="soverview-feature">High-speed internet, filtered water, personal locker</div>
      <div class="soverview-feature">4 guest passes per month (+300 THB for extras)</div>
    </div>

    <p class="soverview-subtitle">
      All bookings follow a fair-use model with peak and off-peak weighting. Peak hours are Monday through Saturday from 10:00 to 18:00. Members can book up to 14 days in advance, with new times released each morning at 07:00.
    </p>

    <div class="soverview-cta">
      <a href="/facility" class="soverview-button">View Facilities</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
